      "summary": "Teri Radichel is the founder of 2nd Sight Lab, AI assisted pentesting and security research. AWS Security Hero since 2016, Author on Amazon and blog, Former IANS & SANS faculty, SANS Difference Makers Award, 30+ years experience in security, software architecture, and software development at companies of all sizes. Security certifications: GSE + 12 more, 2 masters degrees in security engineering and software engineering, BA in business, and has a cute dog. Security, AI, and Technology research blog: https://teriradichel.substack.com Linkedin: https://linkedin.com/in/teriradichel BlueSky, X, Mastodon, Threads, Instragram: @teriradichel",
